Sarri on losing his job: &quot;I spoke to the club a few times in the last days, the problem wasn't so big as you write. I don't know, maybe it wasn't the truth, I don't know. It is not a big problem for me because you are under pressure every six months&quot; <br />
<br />
Sarri on what Spurs win means: &quot;For the relationship with the fans it&rsquo;s a very important match, but I&rsquo;m a coach now we need consistency.&rdquo;

